Package: debian-installer-companion
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1
Description: GTK4 Debian installation companion with hardware checks
 A GTK4/Adwaita application that provides a companion interface
 for the Debian installer. It performs hardware compatibility checks
 and guides users through the installation process.
